## Examples

### Minimal Heartbeat (Low Cost)
```markdown
Check for:
- Critical errors in logs
- System resource usage > 80%
- Unread urgent messages
```

### Comprehensive Heartbeat (Full Monitoring)
```markdown
Monitor all categories:
- System health, security, tasks, development, communication, metrics
- Adaptive frequency based on activity
- Smart alerts with context
```

### Custom Heartbeat (Project-Specific)
```markdown
ClawMaster Development:
- Check CI/CD status
- Monitor test coverage
- Review pending PRs
- Check dependency updates
```

